Subject: [PATCH] drm/sched: Fix deadlock in drm_sched_entity_kill_jobs_cb
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 487df8b698345dd5a91346335f05170ed5f29d4e
